WEBVTT

00:02:26.496 --> 00:02:30.079
boshlanayotgan edi. Va 2010 yilda
marketing ishimdan ayrilganimdan keyin

00:02:30.079 --> 00:02:32.996
hobbiyim to’liq ishimga aylandi.

00:02:32.996 --> 00:02:36.371
Ammo “Men yozuvchiman “ deyishimga
yana ikki yil kerak bo’ldi.

00:02:36.413 --> 00:02:41.621
Yozishni boshlaganimdan to’qqiz yildan
so’ng, men “yozuvchiman”, deya oldim,

00:02:41.663 --> 00:02:44.454
chunki maoshsiz qolishdan,
ayniqsa poyafzal

00:02:44.496 --> 00:02:46.496
xarid qilish odatimni qanday

00:02:46.538 --> 00:02:49.038
davom ettira olishimdan qo’rqardim.
Bu men

00:02:49.038 --> 00:02:50.204
uchun juda muhim.”

00:02:50.246 --> 00:02:51.371
(Kulgi)

00:02:51.371 --> 00:02:54.371
Shunday ekan, bu maqsadga erishish uchun

00:02:54.413 --> 00:02:56.038
uzoq vaqt talab etdi.

00:02:56.079 --> 00:02:57.496
Keyin tushunib yetdimki,

00:02:57.538 --> 00:02:59.829
qo’rquv bizni o’zimizning
maqsadlarimizni

00:02:59.871 --> 00:03:04.038
gapirishdan va bajarishdan
saqlaydigan katta qudratga ega. Va men